Synopsis:
The original Zorro, Don Diego de la Vega, is captured and imprisoned just
as Spain concedes California to Santa Anna. 20 years go by and his 
mortal enemy, Don Rafael Montero, returns to California with a plan to 
become wealthy at the expense of the peasants. The original Zorro 
escapes from prison and trains a new Zorro to take his place.
